Heavenly, formless is the Person (Purusha).
He is without and within, unborn,
Breathless, mindless (a-manas), pure,
Higher than the high Imperishable.

From Him is produced breath,
Mind, and all the senses,
Space, wind, light, water,
And earth, the supporter of all.
